    <p>Most protein tracking apps weren't built for people trying to stay strong after 40. They were built for people trying to lose weight, count every calorie, or optimize every micronutrient. Those are real goals — just not the same goal.</p>

    <p>If you're a man over 40 and your primary objective is preserving muscle mass, the app that matters most is the one aligned with that objective. Here's an honest look at four common options.</p>

