      <p>It was built by a 64-year-old who wanted exactly this — nothing more, nothing less. The simplicity isn't a limitation. Most men over 40 eat the same 8–12 foods each week. You don't need a database of millions. You need a number you can actually hit consistently. Because the habit is the whole game.</p>
      <p>And if you've ever wondered why SnapProtein doesn't have a <a href="https://snapprotein.com/blog/protein-tracker-no-barcode-scanner/" style="color:var(--green);font-weight:600;">barcode scanner</a> — that's intentional too.</p>
